<!--
Instructions for the lab:
_______________________________________________________________________________
1. Download Lab4.html and the image triceratopslogo.jpg. 
2. There are a few css properties in the file, leave them there. Use the css in 
   Chapter 8, on page 289 to create a column layout with a header, main, aside 
   and footer section.
3. In the header, display the image. Next to the image, add a span element with
   class="title". Add content to display your name.
4. In the main section, add the following subtitles: Objectives, Courses 
   Completed, Hobbies, and Favorite Books.
5. Under the Objectives subtitle, add an unordered list your academic and 
   professional goals.
6. Under Courses Completed add an ordered list (with the default list type) 
   with courses you've taken, are taking, or plan to take in the future.
7. Under Hobbies, add an ordered list with list style set to "a" with at 
   least 3 hobbies.
8. Under Favorite Books, add an ordered list with list style set to "i" 
   with at least 3 books.  
9. In the aside, add a link to your github repository under the 
   subtitle "Code Examples".
10. Add an unordered list of organizations that you belong to under the 
    subtitle "Organizations".
11. In the footer, center align your email address.
12. The background should be set to "teal" for the body. The background for 
    any content sections: main, aside, header, footer should be set to "white".
-->
